Coastal cities proved to be a big hit with Yahoo users, as New Orleans, Atlantic City, New Jersey and Key West, Florida rounded out the top five.

They were followed by Ocean City in Maryland, Santa Barbara and San Diego in California, Virginia Beach and San Francisco.

Yahoo says leisure destinations dominated its top ten, with New York and Chicago failing to make the cut.

This year’s list is almost a mirror image of the top ten from 2013, with the top three – Las Vegas, Myrtle Beach and New Orleans – remaining unchanged.

